Package: aqdatapipeline
Title: Download and Process Air Quality Data
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Joseph", "Grealy", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "joseph@example.com")
Description: Downloads air quality data, initially from the UK Automatic Urban
    and Rural Network using openair, stores it as a partitioned local Parquet
    dataset, and calculates daily, monthly, and annual means from hourly
    observations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    arrow,
    dplyr,
    lubridate,
    openair,
    readr,
    rlang,
    tibble
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
